snippet.textDisplay: I downloaded tiktok just to check it out thinking it would be ridiculous. Turnes out I love it. Its seems to have become a safe community for lgbtq+ people and the love and compassion is absolutely amazing. Add in all the extremely talented cosplayers, the educational posts about mental health and disabilities, cute babies and animals and well this app is amazing. I've seen so many people finding joy in being allowed to be themselves, and people showering each other in love for finding the courage to be themselves. It gives me hope, maybe we can make the world a better, more open and loving place
